page.title: 01HOBBIES
page.content: My hobbies are climbing trees and collecting Embassy cigarette coupons. On a night I go climbing trees with my friends. Not far from us there is a wood called Granny Lawson's Wood. It is near the Little Hole (a deep pond). People say that Indians used to live there. Another thing I like doing catching tadpoles and frogs. The Embassy coupons I collect are a kind of money. You can buy things like pens and pencils, paper all sorts of toys and other things. You can buy electric things like hairdryers, vacuum cleaners, tongues - in fact all the things you can think of.
